WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.466 --> 00:00:01.366
Your Majesty, calm your anger.

2
00:00:01.533 --> 00:00:02.666
Preserve your health.

3
00:00:02.966 --> 00:00:06.066
How can I calm down? This fool’s actions are too severe.

4
00:00:06.066 --> 00:00:07.500
How can I calm down?

5
00:00:08.466 --> 00:00:09.433
In the last life,

6
00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:12.300
I actually let this fool raise an army and break into the palace.

7
00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:14.800
This is simply a crime against the ages, Your Majesty.

8
00:00:15.066 --> 00:00:17.833
I understand all the forces Prince Duan had in court,

9
00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:21.033
but I missed a divine physician in Prince Duan’s residence.

10
00:00:21.733 --> 00:00:23.033
Indeed.

11
00:00:23.166 --> 00:00:25.800
This was an unexpected discovery while I was investigating the concubines.

12
00:00:26.166 --> 00:00:27.800
The Soul-Stealing Umbrella is not a rare item.

13
00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:29.800
The medicine that the concubines long gave you,

14
00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:32.300
the Fragrant Blossom Tea,

15
00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:34.466
was specially formulated by that divine physician in Prince Duan’s residence.

16
00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:37.000
He is the only one who can make the antidote.

17
00:00:37.066 --> 00:00:39.700
Since the incident with Prince Duan,

18
00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:41.133
this divine physician has vanished without a trace.

19
00:00:41.133 --> 00:00:42.266
As if he never existed.

20
00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:44.133
Impossible.

21
00:00:44.133 --> 00:00:45.400
The world under heaven is the king’s land.

22
00:00:45.466 --> 00:00:46.933
As long as he is human,

23
00:00:46.933 --> 00:00:48.033
he will leave traces.

24
00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:50.766
Besides the method being poor,

25
00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:53.000
I also found a kind of poison in the concubines’ possessions.

26
00:00:53.133 --> 00:00:54.466
What is Qingzi Soup?

27
00:00:54.666 --> 00:00:56.766
According to the Imperial Medical Department,

28
00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:58.433
this soup is one of the ten forbidden drugs in the palace.

29
00:00:58.700 --> 00:01:00.366
If pregnant,

30
00:01:00.500 --> 00:01:01.966
it will not only cause miscarriage

31
00:01:02.066 --> 00:01:03.266
but the mother will also face severe death.

32
00:01:03.333 --> 00:01:06.366
If not pregnant,

33
00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:07.666
it might result in permanent infertility.

34
00:01:07.766 --> 00:01:08.900
What did you say?

35
00:01:09.066 --> 00:01:11.300
Say it again.

36
00:01:11.933 --> 00:01:13.200
Permanent infertility?

37
00:01:17.300 --> 00:01:19.300
What exactly went wrong?
